room_title: Escape room "Pirate Captain" by Escape Games Riverside in Redlands
room_description: While sailing the Caribbean in the year 1720, tasked with learning the family business, your ship was savagely attacked. You have been captured by pirates! The infamous Captain Bartholomew Roberts "Black Bart" has locked you in his quarters aboard his ship the Royal Fortune. What happens next is up to you... Will you be able to escape before the pirates make you walk the plank?
